snippet.title: Matthew Lanz - brother of Austin Lanz - suspected in couple's murder and police officer's stabbing
snippet.description:
Police said Matthew Lanz, the 22-year-old suspect in the stabbing of a Sandy Springs officer during a home intrusion, was the suspect in the murder of a young couple in Acworth -- Justin and Amber Hicks.

Records show Lanz was the Hicks' neighbor. The couple was found killed in their home on Thursday, Nov. 18. Their 2-year-old son was found in the home unharmed.

Read the full story here - https://www.11alive.com/article/news/crime/matthew-lanz-sandy-springs-police-stabbing-acworth-couple-murder/85-014d32fc-d955-44b2-886b-c9fbb438855b
